                      <h1><center>The perfect business retreat.</center></h1>
                      <p>Good ideas come easier in stimulating environments. That’s the spirit of meetings at The Portofino Hotel & Yacht Club–a luxurious coastal retreat complete with a private marina, swaying palms and warm, Southern Californian charm. With over 8,000 square feet of convention, conference or event space and 8 meeting and banquet rooms, you can expect exceptional versatility and stunning ocean views. For your convenience, we also offer a business center, audiovisual services and a technical assistance staff.</p>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                  <td valign="top" class="rightCol">
                    <div class="contentRight" id="divContentRight">
                      <h2>Los Angeles Meetings At-a-glance</h2>
                      <h3>Hotel Overview</h3>
                      <ul>
                        <li>Los Angeles’ only oceanfront hotel extending into the Pacific on its own private peninsula</li>
                        <li>163 beautifully appointed guestrooms including two suites</li>
                        <li>Unlimited activities including nearby golf, water sports, Catalina Island, Hermosa Beach and exciting Los Angeles</li>
                      </ul>
                      <h3>Los Angeles Meeting Facilities</h3>
                      <ul>
                        <li>Over 8,000 square feet of beautiful convention, conference or event space, including the Bayside and Pacific Ballrooms with floor to ceiling windows overlooking the Pacific Ocean</li>
                        <li>Pool area can accommodate up to 80 guests for an al fresco event</li>
                        <li>High Speed Wireless Internet service</li>
                        <li>Business center</li>
                        <li>Audiovisual services</li>
                      </ul>
